<title>yạ yswʿ hnạk fy ạlṣlyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ yswʿ hnạk fy ạlṣlyb rfʿt ʿny yạ ḥbyb
 yạ ḥbyby tḥmlt ạlạlạ̉m ltmnḥny ạlslạm
 ạlqrạr - fsẖkẖṣk yḥlw lfw̉ạdy wḥbk ymlạ̉ kyạny ạ̉lmsh ạ̉ḥsh yḥyṭ bḥyạty
 fhw gẖdẖạỷy yjry̱ fy dmạỷy bgẖyrh lạ ạstṭyʿ ạlḥyạẗ
 2- fy̱ ṭryq ạljljtẖh ạlrhyb mḍyt tdfʿ ạlqṣạṣ
 ʿndmạ qd tẖmrwạ ydyk ạ̉ṭʿt ftm ạlkẖlạṣ
 3- fy̱ ạlṣlyb rạ̉ytk hnạk tḥbny bqlbk
 yạ yswʿ lm tnsny hnạk bạlrgẖm mn ậlạmk
 4- nẓrh ḥb jạrf qwy jry mn jnbk ạlḍʿyf
 fdmạk tḥml ạlkẖlạṣ lkl kẖạṭyʾ ạ̉tẖym</lyrics>
</song>